{"attributes":{"title":"Signal frequency breakdown","description":"Count of gateway_output turns by pattern signal fired (90d, full history, top 20). Caveat: the recall-cue detector sometimes writes the raw matched user-text verbatim into the signals array instead of a canonical label (e.g. \"Refresh my memory\", \"Going back to earlier\") -- these are one-off strings, not real signal categories, and inflate the apparent diversity of this breakdown. recall_cue_reclassified (5 occurrences) is the canonical marker for those turns; the echoed-text entries are an instrumentation bug, out of scope to fix here.","visualizationType":"lnsDatatable","state":{"visualization":{"layerId":"b1a3b819-8d00-49f2-9dbf-e8566f2fbaff","layerType":"data","columns":[{"columnId":"be13b8ab-f8e8-4a6d-8362-27817e0f74c3"},{"columnId":"258be0ce-06a3-4add-984d-daabf1d21e9c"}]},"query":{"query":"event_type: \"gateway_output\"","language":"kuery"},"filters":[],"datasourceStates":{"formBased":{"layers":{"b1a3b819-8d00-49f2-9dbf-e8566f2fbaff":{"columns":{"be13b8ab-f8e8-4a6d-8362-27817e0f74c3":{"label":"Top 20 values of signals","dataType":"string","operationType":"terms","sourceField":"signals","isBucketed":true,"params":{"size":20,"orderBy":{"type":"column","columnId":"258be0ce-06a3-4add-984d-daabf1d21e9c"},"orderDirection":"desc","otherBucket":true,"missingBucket":false,"parentFormat":{"id":"terms"},"include":[],"exclude":[],"includeIsRegex":false,"excludeIsRegex":false}},"258be0ce-06a3-4add-984d-daabf1d21e9c":{"label":"Count","dataType":"number","operationType":"count","isBucketed":false,"sourceField":"___records___","params":{"emptyAsNull":true},"customLabel":true}},"columnOrder":["be13b8ab-f8e8-4a6d-8362-27817e0f74c3","258be0ce-06a3-4add-984d-daabf1d21e9c"],"incompleteColumns":{},"sampling":1}}},"indexpattern":{"layers":{}},"textBased":{"layers":{}}},"internalReferences":[],"adHocDataViews":{}}},"references":[{"type":"index-pattern","id":"agent-logs-pattern","name":"indexpattern-datasource-laye