{"attributes":{"title":"Reclassification events","description":"This is the only misclassification-correction signal visible in gateway_output telemetry: turns where a memory-recall cue pattern overrode the initial classification (signals contains recall_cue_reclassified), broken down by the corrected task_type. Rare -- 5 of 1696 turns (0.3%) over the full 90d/77-day emission history, all on 2026-05-10, all corrected to memory_recall. A separate recall_controller_skipped event (503 docs, out of scope here) logs the recall controller's decision-not-to-override cases with an original_task_type field, offering a richer decision-log for this subsystem if a deeper investigation is warranted later.","visualizationType":"lnsDatatable","state":{"visualization":{"layerId":"f6a3afdd-86d6-4c8f-a307-0c9f2dba9b9c","layerType":"data","columns":[{"columnId":"ff88d8a3-5dd8-4408-8b98-dda5361fd6c4"},{"columnId":"0fc2b36f-c60c-4127-8b87-8d2b99d41bea"}]},"query":{"query":"event_type: \"gateway_output\" and signals: \"recall_cue_reclassified\"","language":"kuery"},"filters":[],"datasourceStates":{"formBased":{"layers":{"f6a3afdd-86d6-4c8f-a307-0c9f2dba9b9c":{"columns":{"ff88d8a3-5dd8-4408-8b98-dda5361fd6c4":{"label":"Top 5 values of task_type","dataType":"string","operationType":"terms","sourceField":"task_type","isBucketed":true,"params":{"size":5,"orderBy":{"type":"column","columnId":"0fc2b36f-c60c-4127-8b87-8d2b99d41bea"},"orderDirection":"desc","otherBucket":true,"missingBucket":false,"parentFormat":{"id":"terms"},"include":[],"exclude":[],"includeIsRegex":false,"excludeIsRegex":false}},"0fc2b36f-c60c-4127-8b87-8d2b99d41bea":{"label":"Reclassified turns","dataType":"number","operationType":"count","isBucketed":false,"sourceField":"___records___","params":{"emptyAsNull":true},"customLabel":true}},"columnOrder":["ff88d8a3-5dd8-4408-8b98-dda5361fd6c4","0fc2b36f-c60c-4127-8b87-8d2b99d41bea"],"incompleteColumns":{},"sampling":1}}},"indexpattern":{"layers":{}},"textBased":{"layers":{}}},"